      "text": "やったー！　すみれちゃん、よろしくね！\nじゃあ、もう一人は～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Thanks‚ Sumire-chan!\nSo‚ the other person is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
